1943
01:11:12,757 --> 01:11:13,986
Awak boleh baring di sini. Apa pendapat anda?

1944
01:11:13,987 --> 01:11:14,987
(sini)

1945
01:11:14,988 --> 01:11:16,227
Mereka tidak boleh sampai sejauh ini.

1946
01:11:16,927 --> 01:11:18,057
Ia tidak teruk.

1947
01:11:19,327 --> 01:11:20,327
Cepatlah.

1948
01:11:20,328 --> 01:11:23,667
